## 7. Core Features (MVP)

### 7.1 Activity Control

* Start walking/running session
* Stop session at any time
* Clear visual state change between idle and active

### 7.2 Real-Time Location Tracking

* Uses browser Geolocation API
* Tracks user movement only during active sessions
* Updates location every few seconds

### 7.3 Map Visualization

* Real-world interactive map
* Path drawn smoothly as user moves
* Map centers on user‚Äôs current position
* Completed paths remain visible after session

### 7.4 Live Metrics Display

Displayed subtly on screen:

* Elapsed time
* Total distance (km)

### 7.5 Session Summary

After stopping:

* Distance covered
* Time spent
* Visual replay of the path

