## 9. Visual Design System

### Color Palette

* Background: Dark gray / deep blue
* Primary accent: Mint / cyan
* Secondary accent: Soft white
* Path color: Bright but subtle (gold, cyan)

### Typography

* Headings: Bold, rounded sans-serif
* Body text: Clean, modern font
* Metrics: Monospaced or numeric-friendly font

### Animations

* Button morphing (Start ‚Üí Stop)
* Smooth path drawing
* Fade/slide transitions between states

---

## 10. Non-Functional Requirements

### Performance

* Fast load time
* Smooth map rendering
* Minimal re-renders

### Privacy

* Location data used only during active session
* No background tracking
* No public sharing of paths
* Data stored locally (MVP)

### Reliability

* Graceful handling of location permission denial
* Works on modern browsers

---

## 11. Technical Architecture

### Tech Stack

* Frontend: React (Vite / Next.js)
* Maps: Mapbox GL JS
* Location: Browser Geolocation API
* State Management: React state/hooks
* Storage (optional): localStorage

