## 14. Risks & Mitigation

| Risk              | Mitigation                  |
| ----------------- | --------------------------- |
| GPS noise         | Ignore very small movements |
| Battery usage     | Throttle location updates   |
| Permission denial | Clear fallback UI           |
| UI clutter        | Strict MVP feature control  |

